headline: Should You Buy Cava Stock Before Feb. 25?
summary: The market has been all over Cava Group (NYSE: CAVA) stock since it debuted as a public company in early 2023.  Investors might be wary about just how good its earnings results are going to be when it reports on Feb. 25, especially considering how much growth is already built into its stock price.  Cava is one of the newer fast-casual restaurant chains that have stormed the markets in recent years.
